.  SOURCE CODE FOR THE XE VERSION OF THE SIC FAMILY OF COMPUTER
.  This tests label usage (ex: MOVECH), index addressing (ex: STR1, X), immediate addressing (ex: #11) BYTE, RESB, WORD, format 2 (ex: TIXR)
TEST3     START   0
          LDT     ELEVEN
          LDX    #0
MOVECH    LDCH    STR1, X
          STCH    STR2, X
          TIXR    T
          JLT     MOVECH
          RSUB

STR1      BYTE    C'TEST STRING'
STR2      RESB    11
ELEVEN    WORD    11
          END     TEST3


